"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"*This article explains how you can create a MetaMask wallet that can store cryptocurrency and NFTs.*\\n\\n**Follow these instructions to set up your MetaMask wallet:**\\n\\n1. **[Click here to download MetaMask](https://metamask.io/download/)** using mobile application or desktop browser extension\\n2. Open the application and get started to **create a new wallet**\\n3. **Set your password** for your new wallet\\n4. **Write down your seed phrase**. It is best to store this written on a safe piece of paper or device that is not connected to the internet. If you forget your password, you can reset it by importing your wallet using your seed phrase. If you loose your seed phrase, it can never be recovered.\\n5. **Complete the seed phrase verification** and account setup steps and voila, you now have a cryptocurrency wallet that supports storing NFTs!\\n\\n## Helpful Hints\\n\\n**Hint 1 - Your public wallet address is the unique identifier for your wallet.** You can easily copy it from below you account name or from the MetaMask menu options.\\n\\n![Where yo view your public wallet address](https://mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2FxC9Etz4G5PF4-RgvOHZK7.jpg&w=3840&q=90)\\n\\nWhere yo view your public wallet address\\n\\n**Hint 2 - Never share you seed phrase or private key.** These should always be kept private, anyone with them can access all assets within the wallet.\\n\\n**Hint 3 -** **We recommended also setting up the MetaMask browser extension** for an easier experience interacting with websites.\\n\\n**Hint 4 - Pin the MetaMask browser extension to your chrome taskbar.** You can open the the wallet from your browser’s extension menu and pin it to your taskbar for easy access.\\n\\n![Screenshot of how to open MetaMask using the Google Chrome extension](https://mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2F4BMSVyhTXzXw9swFJU13s.png&w=1920&q=90)\\n\\nScreenshot of how to open MetaMask using the Google Chrome extension\\n\\n![MetaMask is now pinned to your taskbar](https://mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2FLjjyTxNLlzG5SO_a7srPT.png&w=1080&q=90)\\n\\nMetaMask is now pinned to your taskbar\\n\\n## View step by step screenshots below\\n\\n*Updated January 20th, 2022 - screenshots cover downloading the MetaMask Chrome browser extension*\\n\\n### 1) Click here to download MetaMask using the desktop browser extension\\n\\n![Select \\\"install MetaMask for Chrome\\\"](https://mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2Fm2ePa207jD1ilrQMMtlda.png&w=3840&q=90)\\n\\nSelect \\\"install MetaMask for Chrome\\\"\\n\\nAdd [the MetaMask chrome extension](https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/metamask/nkbihfbeogaeaoehlefnkodbefgpgknn) to your browser\\n\\n![select \\\"Add to Chrome\\\"](https://mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2F2Z01ixbKlgVnHrfDuRixX.jpg&w=3840&q=90)\\n\\nselect \\\"Add to Chrome\\\"\\n\\n![Select \\\"Add extension\\\"](https://mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2FgMyOsg5YO1Hnb2rDZbX4T.jpg&w=1920&q=90)\\n\\nSelect \\\"Add extension\\\"\\n\\n### 2) Open the application and get started to create a new wallet\\n\\n![Select \\\"Get Started\\\"](https://mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2FwKFNi0AGdIZK3xGhdqwCz.jpg&w=1920&q=90)\\n\\nSelect \\\"Get Started\\\"\\n\\n![Select \\\"I Agree\\\"](https://mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2FSi6-BDP39qYnIhweWji-i.jpg&w=3840&q=90)\\n\\nSelect \\\"I Agree\\\"\\n\\n### 3) Set your password for your new wallet\\n\\n![Set your password and agree to the terms](https://mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2FckfmH9bkgiNTPzPNUQMNI.jpg&w=1920&q=90)\\n\\nSet your password and agree to the terms\\n\\n### 4) Write down your seed phrase.\\n\\nIt is best to store this written on a safe piece of paper or device that is not connected to the internet. If you forget your password, you can reset it by importing your wallet using your seed phrase. If you loose your seed phrase, it can never be recovered.\\n\\n![](https://mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2FXomdz4G6tQVt6OpFVwjKb.jpg&w=3840&q=90)\\n\\n![](https://mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2FY_rxMI8I_FWM2qPacf4hD.jpg&w=3840&q=90)\\n\\n### 5) Complete the seed phrase verification and account setup steps\\n\\n… and voila, you now have a cryptocurrency wallet that supports storing NFTs!\\n\\n![](https://mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2FjALZmhhpaOA-zAWc031HZ.jpg&w=3840&q=90)\\n\\nYou can now deposit ETH to your new MetaMask wallet by transferring it in, or buying it from an option offered within the application\\n\\n![](https://mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2FboS1RabGEzUikVNw2CTop.jpg&w=3840&q=90)\\n\\n> Learn more about How to Buy NFTs here.\",\"timestamp\":1642671665,\"title\":\"How to create a MetaMask wallet\"},\"digest\":\"Y0V3Q2z1NvNV7ghWuNvSuqtpCPnKHv-ezDONPGkO4jI\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x5056596726deAcAA6a78Ad4f1bB826d008689606\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"sOuV983r5KC3mMgUt6lwHxpSh98Irc9LRL5kAA5yPQY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Tc8itbnJuOsmIdiGa6lDYe6rVVweQ_uTEODW_0HQJt4\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"stonmUCyTl5_CZcdWuasvC8jpNg9-3pZSdAqBsPgJ1eFv_RYifeHW095sr0sa7oHzDqiNZODnshX7C_veRZrQA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x437e72951c439881e4f77d6ad8e87a126213d0dd8ba8d2bd5b8ea1c5928e9ac452a548eb879a86f76c01e1fafb59e0de222116e229ccb65dbeb012accac